                            <comment id="14957542" author="chengas123" created="Wed, 14 Oct 2015 19:11:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;jai-imageio was moved to to github and bintray. You might be interested in jai-imageio-core 1.3.0 which is relased in Maven Central. See &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/jai-imageio/jai-imageio-core&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/jai-imageio/jai-imageio-core&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

